  "title": "Electrician / Light fittings Installer",
  "description": "<p>Job Summary:<br />The Installer will be responsible for installation of light fittings and fabric cover with accessories (inclusive installing aluminium bracket). The Installer needs to be familiar with the electrical code of practice (SS 638 : 2018) and ensure its compliance.<br /><br />Requirements:</p><ul><li>2 years or more experience in electrical installation (experience working in project is an advantage)</li><li>Able to read electrical and shop drawing</li><li>Good interpersonal skills and able to work with minimum supervision</li><li>Detail oriented and able to work in a tight schedule.</li><li>Preferably possess own transport (Allowance will be provided)</li><li>Able to start work immediately.</li></ul><p>Other Information:</p><ul><li>5.5-day work week (Mon to Fri: 9am to 6pm, Saturday 9am to 1pm), MUST be ready to work for after office hours Installation, Overtime will be paid.</li><li>Work Location : Islandwide (Office in Tai Seng)</li></ul><p>Please send the detailed resume with your expected salary to <a href=\"mailto:sales@alcoshading.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">sales@alcoshading.com</a>. Kindly note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
